const n='---\ntitle: "Posts & Blog API"\ndescription: "Endpoints for managing and retrieving blog posts and articles."\n---\n\n# Posts & Blog API\n\nThis section describes the API endpoints for managing and retrieving blog posts, announcements, and pages.\n\n## Public Endpoints\n\n### List Posts\n\nRetrieve a list of active posts, optionally filtered by type.\n\n**Endpoint:** `GET /api/posts`\n\n**Query Parameters:**\n\n- `type` (optional): Filter by post type (e.g., `blog`, `announcement`, `page`). Defaults to `blog`.\n\n**Response:**\n\n```json\n[\n  {\n    "id": 1,\n    "slug": "getting-started",\n    "title": "Getting Started with APayShop",\n    "description": "Learn how to set up your store in minutes.",\n    "imageUrl": "https://example.com/image.jpg",\n    "type": "blog",\n    "createdAt": "2024-01-01T00:00:00.000Z",\n    "updatedAt": "2024-01-02T00:00:00.000Z"\n  }\n]\n```\n\n### Get Post by Slug\n\nRetrieve a single active post by its unique slug.\n\n**Endpoint:** `GET /api/posts/:slug`\n\n**Response:**\n\n```json\n{\n  "id": 1,\n  "slug": "getting-started",\n  "title": "Getting Started with APayShop",\n  "content": "<p>This is the full HTML content of the post...</p>",\n  "description": "Learn how to set up your store in minutes.",\n  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/image.jpg",\n  "type": "blog",\n  "isActive": true,\n  "metaData": null,\n  "createdAt": "2024-01-01T00:00:00.000Z",\n  "updatedAt": "2024-01-02T00:00:00.000Z"\n}\n```\n\n---\n\n## Admin Endpoints (Requires Authentication)\n\n### List All Posts\n\nRetrieve a paginated list of all posts, including drafts.\n\n**Endpoint:** `GET /api/admin/posts`\n\n### Create Post\n\nCreate a new post.\n\n**Endpoint:** `POST /api/admin/posts`\n\n**Body:**\n\n```json\n{\n  "slug": "new-announcement",\n  "title": "New Feature Release",\n  "description": "We just released a great new feature.",\n  "content": "<p>Details here...</p>",\n  "type": "announcement",\n  "imageUrl": "https://example.com/image2.jpg",\n  "isActive": true\n}\n```\n\n### Update Post\n\nUpdate an existing post.\n\n**Endpoint:** `PUT /api/admin/posts/:id`\n\n### Delete Post\n\nDelete a post permanently.\n\n**Endpoint:** `DELETE /api/admin/posts/:id`\n';export{n as default};
